subject: Basketball (College)
Coaches and Managers
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Eddie Jordan, a former Scarlet Knights star who went on to play and coach in the N.B.A., did not graduate from the university, although its Web site said he had.
